00:56:01,068 --> 00:56:06,573
<i>Le clown</i>
<i>Dont la culotte fait boum</i>

697
00:56:06,782 --> 00:56:09,076
<i>Ou la danse</i>

698
00:56:09,701 --> 00:56:12,496
<i>Où l'on rêve de romance</i>

699
00:56:12,704 --> 00:56:15,082
<i>Ou la scène</i>

700
00:56:15,540 --> 00:56:18,794
<i>Où la teigne crache sa haine</i>

701
00:56:20,128 --> 00:56:24,091
<i>C'est divertissant</i>

702
00:56:27,094 --> 00:56:28,720
<i>Les spots</i>

703
00:56:29,971 --> 00:56:32,307
<i>Sur la belle dame en short</i>

704
00:56:32,474 --> 00:56:34,810
<i>La mariée</i>

705
00:56:35,060 --> 00:56:37,437
<i>Qui a un autre bien-aimé</i>

706
00:56:37,604 --> 00:56:39,981
<i>Ou le bal</i>

707
00:56:40,565 --> 00:56:44,361
<i>Où enfin elle se dévoile</i>

708
00:56:45,445 --> 00:56:49,324
